{"tid":1658894,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"睇到好撚嬲，你班連登仔咁撚易比人帶到風向，講咩光復香港時代革命？","createTime":"2019-10-16T16:10:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T15:27:50.000Z","uid":23721,"like":52,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"f4aaa63c5e884e82a3087c8e72e08950775b8e87","tid":1658894,"uid":23721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:10:01.000Z","msg":"見好撚多人話唔帶裝，全和平遊行<br />\n咪撚on9得唔得<br />\n上唔上裝一件事，裝一定要帶<br />\n去到10月中都仲叫人唔帶裝係咩料？<br />\n唔係叫你送頭，大家裝修完，玩完玩具咪閃人囉<br />\n唔需要打陣地，hit and run, be water.<br />\n叫人唔帶裝嘅係泛民打手定點呀屌你老母<br />\n你班撚樣想割蓆好撚耐啦<br />\n又叫人和平呀乜乜柒柒，想要返主導權？<br />\n我話你地知，無人有主導權，無人係大台<br />\n想收割運動成果？得，下世先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又，乜撚嘢勇武同裝修會令法案唔通過？今朝眾議院一致通過喎<br />\n係，仲有參議院一關要過，但參議院唔係鐵板一塊，一兩個人走埋嚟話裝修勇武會阻法案通過，佢兩個代表晒咁撚多人呀？都仲未計佢地議會內部嘅權勢關係，你班友咪撚柒啦<br />\n<br />\n泛民想割蓆好耐啦，咁鍾意割，定你想比人割頸嘅唔係狗係你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"060fd76f05d3e6846fbf98fa8ea8c81591b3f747","tid":1658894,"uid":23721,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:10:24.000Z","msg":"屌你老母睇到好撚嬲"},{"pid":"3020465a229aa2e68605524601367e23697bd02f","tid":1658894,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:11:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PgjbDGh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPgjbDGh.jpg&h=e5447ac9&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"7f3c5c958362d38fe0d2d32a64e6d2872cdc3350","tid":1658894,"uid":23721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3020465a229aa2e68605524601367e23697bd02f","tid":1658894,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:11:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PgjbDGh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPgjbDGh.jpg&h=e5447ac9&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:11:48.000Z","msg":"齊上齊落，加油